description: To develop a Python-based GUI application for real-time speech-to-text transcription using the OpenAI Whisper API on OpenSUSE Linux, here is a high-level plan to guide you throughout the development process:
Cohere Command R Plus 0824 - Via Hugging Face Chat
Deep Seek Via Chatbox (Desktop UI), API Integration
Gemini 1.5 Pro Via Google AI Studio
Meta Llama 3.3 70B Instruct (Via Hugging Face Chat)
Nova Pro 1o (Via Open Router web UI)
Qwen 2.5 Coder 32B Instruct Via Open Web UI (Via Open Router)
Qwen 2.5 Coder 32B Instruct Via Hugging Face Chat
Qwen 72B Instruct - Via Hugging Face Chat
Claude 3.5 Sonnet Latest - Via LibreChat (API Integration)
